| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1265 — Recovery Inhibition (payoutsking)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 96045015-74c9-5cf9-a2fb-fbfe30f9df4c"
